function Start()
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(id_Villager)
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(id_Villager)
	
	-- Walk off and delete
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, marker_walk_to, "npc_walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idClone, 1.0)
	end
end

function Start()
	idSelf = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_Callout, idSelf, id_Villager)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Remove potion dose
	Hydra.PlayerGrantPotionDose(idActorPlayer, -1)
end
